name: A Dogfight Combat Shooter - Modern Jet Fighter Game HD Free
name_original: A Dogfight Combat Shooter - Modern Jet Fighter Game HD Free
description:
Arcade style air combat with real-life HD graphics!
____________________________________________

Take control of the sky with modern combat aircrafts!
____________________________________________

You can destroy or dodge enemy missiles and fighter jets as you earn stars to unlock planes.

Gameplay becomes more and more challenging as enemy approach you faster and faster.

Challenge a friend to see who can earn the most points.
____________________________________________

3 different fighter jets to choose from:
• F-14 – Tomcat
• F-22 – Raptor
• F-117 – Nighthawk
